### Test BFF Endpoints - Inventory System
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health HTTP/1.1

###

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/productos HTTP/1.1

###

### Get Product by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/productos/1 HTTP/1.1

###

### Create New Product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/productos HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sku": "TEST-001",
    "nombre": "Producto de Prueba",
    "descripcion": "Producto creado desde REST Client",
    "stock": 15,
    "stock_minimo": 3,
    "stock_maximo": 100,
    "precio": 25990.0,
    "categoria_id": 1,
    "bodega_id": 1,
    "estado": "ACTIVO",
    "unidad_medida": "UNIDAD",
    "peso": 1.5,
    "dimensiones": "20x15x10 cm"
}

###

### Update Product by ID
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/productos/1 HTTP/1.1
